Package: khandaq-messenger
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Khandaq <support@khandaq.org>
Homepage: https://khandaq.org
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), libgcc-s1, libstdc++6, libx11-6, libxcb1, libglib2.0-0
Recommends: libpulse0 | pipewire-pulse, libv4l-0
Description: Khandaq Messenger — decentralized encrypted Tox client
 Khandaq is an open-source messenger using the Tox protocol.
 Messages are end-to-end encrypted and routed peer-to-peer.
 .
 This package bundles Qt and media libraries; no separate Qt install required.
